name: Ralph Barendse
description:
'''Ralph Barendse''' ({{IPA|nl|ˈrɑl(ə)v ˈbaːrəntsə}}, born 6 April 1977) is a Dutch [[disc jockey|DJ]] and producer of [[electronic dance music]], mainly [[Trance music|trance]], performing as '''Ralphie B''' and '''Midway'''. Barendse has also produced remixes for artists in the scene, among them [[Armin van Buuren]], [[Tiësto]], [[Solarstone]], Dario G, and [[4 Strings]]. Barendse's original releases have also been remixed by other artists, including [[Paul van Dyk]], [[Ronski Speed]], Filterheadz, and D. Ramirez.

As a DJ, Barendse has toured, including with Tiësto. Since 2011, Barendse has released several singles under the record label Armada Music.
